  "subject": "OOM-1567: Casablanca SO Enabling debug SO-BPMN",
  "commit_message": "OOM-1567: Casablanca SO Enabling debug SO-BPMN\n\n----------------\nWorking on an Alternate solution;\nThis is a Work In Progress, please DO NOT MERGE\n---------------\nSO:\nEnabling debug params in SO-BPMN-INFRA\nPassing JVM_ARGS to the deployment and introducing\na nodePort so we can debug bpmn infra\n\nIncorporating the comment from Borislav and Prudence\nWe now enable so-debug only if the it's enabled.\n\nChange-Id: I50a55123928bcfe0c6edc01028f9fde2456676d3\nIssue-ID: OOM-1567\nSigned-off-by: Rahul Sharma <Rahul.Sharma2@amdocs.com>\n",
